  "texts": [
    "Identified gaps and directions for future workThere are several limitations to our review as well as identified gaps to direct future research.",
    "First, our review does not include grey literature, which may contain other relevant or more recent work on RAI.",
    "Similarly, there may be other RAI initiatives or practices that are not documented or published as articles and thus are not found in our search.",
    "As a result, our findings may not reflect certain emerging, innovative, or context-specific RAI practices, such as those reported in industry reports, governmental publications, or technical reports.",
    "This omission could result in a narrower view of the full spectrum of RAI practices and their implementation in real-world settings."
  ],
